building an aoo that tracks todo items

this app will have 5 routes that do the following

1. Adding an items

POST /items
{
"lable": "feed tha cat",
"notes" :"the cat really likes tuna, but she is only allowed 1 can a week.

}

2. List all items
   GET / items
   return an array of akk the items

3. Get an item
   GET / item/id

4.

---

internally to the app we want to store items. and we want to track the follwing about them
|
|id: uniquely identidies the items
|lable: this is general summary of the item
|notes: notes about this item
|done: true if the item is done, false if not done
